des:
Tech Home products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light.

There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show.
After connecting Alexa to your Tech Home products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our " Tech Home" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Tech Home account in our " Tech Home" app;
(3). You need to have some Tech Home devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our " Tech Home" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Tech Home" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Tech Home" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Tech Home", and you'll be navigated to Tech Home login page;
(9). Input your Tech Home account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the plug.”
“Alexa,turn off the plug.”

If you experience any problems while using this skill, please contact us at support.us@techhome.com
